source.name: Registered Property in Washington DC
source.description: Registered Property. The dataset contains attributes of registered properties from the Office of Tax and Revenue (OTR), created as part of the Citywide Data Warehouse Program (CityDW) for the D.C. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) and participating D.C. government agencies.
